<A NAME=130Cal-am dam costs>
<H3><IMG SRC=script.gif ALIGN=left HSPACE=5>Cal-am dam costs</H3><BR>
THE CAL-AM WATER COMPANY RELEASED ITS UPDATED COST FIGURES FOR THE PROPOSED CARMEL RIVER DAM AND RESERVOIR.
<P>
